<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MapleSMP | ยินดีต้อนรับ</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/welcome.css">
    <style>
        .site-logo {
            max-width: 420px;
            width: 550px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(100, 200, 255, 0.4));
            animation: logoFloat 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes logoFloat {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50%       { transform: translateY(-8px); }
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kanit:wght@300;500;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logoweb.png">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="welcome-container">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="MAPLESMP Logo" class="site-logo">
        
        <div class="slider-container" id="sliderContainer">
            <div class="slider-bg" id="sliderBg"></div>
            <div class="slider-text">ลากเพื่อเข้าสู่เว็บไซต์</div>
            <div class="slider-thumb" id="sliderThumb">>></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/welcome.js"></script>
</body>
</html>